snippet.textDisplay:
Salutări și multă iubire din România (Craiova). Felicitări pentru toată munca depusă, sunteți super! Țineți-o tot așa! <3
*Translate: "Greetings and much love from Romania (Craiova). Congratulations for everything you've done, you are all amazing! Keep up the good work! <3"*

LE: I have unexpectedly discoverd you from a friend who was listening to Perspektiva in our locker room before a football match. Then I started to listen to you and find other cool songs like Budjav Lebac ... and the best thing was when you guys came in Romania at Open Camp Vaslui, I traveled around 560 KM from Craiova to Vaslui just to see you guys performing live! Since then I am in love with your music style, lyrics, everything. Thank youuu! :)
